Niger Calls for Help in Aiding Refugees From Libya, Sahel Says

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-04-27T11:39:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/niger-calls-for-help-in-aiding-refugees-from-libya-sahel-says.html
Niger needs help from international
donors to manage the West African refugees that have fled
violence in  Libya , state-owned Tele Sahel reported, citing Marou
Amadou, the government spokesman.  The country needs help in repatriating the refugees,
managing their settlements and dealing with health concerns,
Amadou was quoted as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Djibril Saidou via Accra at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  